videos.description: Georgia Tech's Ben Lammers capitalizes on Josh Okogie's miss by slamming home a put-back dunk.
videos.headline: Ben Lammers throws down a put-back dunk for Georgia Tech

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Tadric Jackson hits a 3-pointer at the buzzer to cut Syracuse's lead to 32-29 at the end of the half.
videos.headline: Tadric Jackson hits a buzzer-beater from deep 3-point range

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Tadric Jackson knocks down another 3-pointer to give Georgia Tech ten unanswered points against Syracuse.
videos.headline: Jackson 3-pointer gives Georgia Tech a 10-0 run

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Ben Lammers rejecting Syracuse's Tyler Lydon at the rim for his sixth block of the game.
videos.headline: Lammers gets his sixth block of the night

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Quinton Stephens finds an open Ben Lammers for the alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Lammers hammers home an alley-oop slam

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Tadric Jackson and Josh Okogie throw down dunks to extend Georgia Tech's lead over Syracuse.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech keeps up intensity with a pair of powerful dunks

videos.description: Syracuse's John Gillon makes a corner 3-pointer to cut Georgia Tech's lead to 67-64.
videos.headline: Syracuse makes it a three point game after crazy sequence
